Professional Certificate - 7 course series

Knowing the basics is good, but being fluent is invaluable. The Google AI Professional Certificate takes you beyond foundational understanding to becoming AI-fluent. Designed by Google experts, this program gets you hands-on experience building the AI skills that employers are looking for.

No more guesswork. The curriculum was built by mapping AI capabilities to the skills the job market demands, and validated by employers. Youll learn the fundamentals of AI, including how to prompt and use AI responsibly. Then, youll apply AI to the six domains where AI is transforming work.

In 20+ hands-on activities, youll build a portfolio of job-ready solutions:

  • Brainstorming and Planning: Turn project briefs into detailed workback plans.

  • Research and Insights: Scour sources to create compelling reports.

  • Writing and Communicating: Adapt your communications for multiple audiences.

  • Content Creation: Transform creative visions into custom marketing videos.

  • Data Analysis: Clean messy data and uncover trends using natural language. 

  • App Building: Build a custom AI tool without writing a single line of code. 

Plus, youll build your portfolio with a 3-month no-cost trial of Google AI Pro (terms apply). Gain access to Googles most capable AI models, upgrade your professional toolkit, and do your best work.

Enroll today to master AI skills you can put to use right away, and earn a Google certificate that proves youre ready to deliver results from day one.

Applied Learning Project

This certificate isnt theoretical; youll learn by building job-ready solutions you can put to work immediately, all while following expert-led video tutorials. Our modular design empowers you to customize your learning journey so you can jump straight into the projects most relevant to your workwhether you need to uncover insights from messy data or streamline communications. Through 20+ hands-on activities, you will master practical ways to:

  • Drive strategic outcomes: Use AI as a thought partner to turn rough concepts into actionable project plans and comprehensive research reports.

  • Boost creativity: Rapidly brainstorm marketing materials and transform them into professional-grade images, videos, and engaging presentations.

  • Tackle routine tasks: Streamline your daily workflow by using AI to clean messy data, generate action plans, and build your own custom apps.

By the end of the certificate, youll be ready to succeed in the AI-enabled economy.

AI Fundamentals

Course 1 3 hours

What you'll learn

  • Understand fundamental generative AI concepts and build a foundation for professional AI use. 

  • Construct effective prompts using a structured framework to generate high-quality, relevant outputs for workplace tasks.

  • Evaluate AI-generated outputs for accuracy and bias and apply critical thinking to ensure responsible and ethical AI use. 

  • Analyze your professional workflow to identify high-impact opportunities to collaborate with AI.

Frequently asked questions

The Google AI Professional Certificate teaches you how to move from basic AI knowledge to becoming AI-fluent, no previous experience required. Its built by Google experts and gives you practical experience developing the AI skills employers are looking for. Youll apply AI in areas like brainstorming, planning, research, writing, content creation, data analysis, and coding.

We looked at real job posting data and collaborated with some of Americas largest employers to make sure were teaching you the most in-demand AI skills. Youll learn directly from Google experts who use AI every day. Plus, youll gain three months of no-cost access to Google AI Pro, allowing you to use Googles most capable models to practice your new skills right away. Learn on your own schedule and focus on using AI for the specific areas that matter most to you.

Yes. This certificate includes over 20 hands-on activities where you create job-ready solutions you can use at work. Examples include turning project briefs into workback plans, producing research reports, adapting communications for different audiences, analyzing data using natural language, and building a custom AI tool without needing to code.

Yes. Youll learn the fundamentals of AI, including how to prompt, and youll practice giving AI clear and specific instructions. You'll also learn how to use AI responsibly and build your confidence by using AI thoughtfully across workplace scenarios.

The Google AI Professional Certificate is made up of seven courses that can be completed in about an hour each. You can complete the entire program at your own pace.

After you complete all seven courses, youll earn a certificate from Google to share with your network and potential employers.

This certificate prepares you to use AI at work, a skill set that 70% of managers believe is critical for their organizations success. Youll learn how AI tools can improve how you workallowing you to handle tasks more efficiently and produce higher-quality results.

This certificate is available globally in English, with additional languages coming soon.

Youll practice using Gemini (including Canvas and Deep Research), NotebookLM, and Gemini in Google Workspace (Docs, Slides, Sheets) to level up your daily tasks. You will also build a custom AI tool using Google AI Studio. Youll get three months of no-cost access to Google AI Pro, so you can gain hands-on experience with Googles most advanced models.

In the U.S. and Canada, the subscription cost is $49 per month. Prices may vary in other countries. When you purchase the Google AI Professional Certificate, youll have access to all course materials, including videos, activities, readings, and graded assessments. After you complete all seven courses, youll earn a certificate from Google to share with your professional network and potential employers.

There are no prerequisites, you dont need any experience with AI to get started.

Yes, it is completely safe. Saritasa is an authorized technical partner working with Google to securely generate and distribute your unique Google AI Pro trial codes.

While the initial window is hosted by Saritasa to manage the code distribution, the actual redemption processwhere you enter your information and activate your trialtakes place entirely within the one.google.com domain. Your sensitive account information is handled directly by Googles secure infrastructure, and Saritasa does not have access to your Google Account credentials.

This course is completely online, so theres no need to show up to a classroom in person. You can access your lectures, readings and assignments anytime and anywhere via the web or your mobile device.

Yes! To get started, click the course card that interests you and enroll. You can enroll and complete the course to earn a shareable certificate.
